data.description: Welcome to this spacious 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home with a workshop that is nestled on a generous half-acre lot.  This home features two expansive living areas, two dining areas offering abundant space for both relaxation and social gatherings.  The converted garage provides a versatile space for an additional room, office, gym or additional living area catering to various lifestyle needs.  Step outside to the backyard oasis, complete with a built-in pool, gazebo, and a deck that overlooks the beautiful backyard creating a perfect setting for outdoor entertainment and recreation.  This property seamlessly combines indoor comfort with outdoor leisure making it an ideal haven for both relaxation and entertainment.
